{"id": "5475", "post": "<div class=\"post-5475 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-virtual-servers tag-buffalo tag-exclusive tag-openvz tag-usa\" id=\"post-5475\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/virmach-first-month-free-vps-1month-after-and-more-starting-at-1-95month-for-128mb-in-buffalo/\" rel=\"bookmark\">VirMach \u2013 First month free VPS ($1/month after) and more starting at $1.95/month for 128MB in Buffalo</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/buffalo/\" rel=\"tag\">buffalo</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/exclusive/\" rel=\"tag\">exclusive</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/openvz/\" rel=\"tag\">openvz</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/usa/\" rel=\"tag\">USA</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \"> July 11, 2014 @ 1:00 pm, by Maarten Kossen</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><a href=\"http://virmach.com\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIzMDAiIGhlaWdodD0iMTg4IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgMzAwIDE4OCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"screenshot\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Homepage_VirMach.comVirMach.com_Premium_yet_affordable_VPS_hosting_-_2014-07-11_06.18.27-300x188.png.webp\" alt=\"Homepage_VirMach.comVirMach.com_Premium_yet_affordable_VPS_hosting_-_2014-07-11_06.18.27\" width=\"300\" height=\"188\"></a>Amir, from <a href=\"http://virmach.com\">VirMach</a>, has sent in these exclusive offers for LowEndBox readers. VirMach is quite a new company having opened shop little over a month ago. Amir runs the company with a partner and has registered an LLC in the state of Oklahoma, where VirMach resides. These offers are hosted on a host node with an E3-1240v2 CPU, 32GB of RAM, and 4x 512GB SSD drives configured in RAID10 backed up by a RAID card. The server is rented through Hudson Valley Host which is part of ColoCrossing. VirMach has two sister companies; vpsgamers.com and vpscraft.com which also seem to revolve around VPS hosting. They do offer a 24-hours 100% money back guarantee and work on refund requests on a case-by-case basis outside of that period. The free month special is limited to the first 50 signups, so be quick to grab one of those if you want to! As usual, please leave your feedback here in the comments or at LowEndTalk!</p><p><strong>The offers</strong></p><table><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\"><strong>Special #1</strong><p></p><ul><li>1 CPU core</li><li>64MB RAM</li><li>128MB Burst</li><li>2GB SSD space</li><li>20GB traffic</li><li>5Mbps uplink</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>OpenVZ/SolusVM</li><li><strong>1st month free</strong></li><li>Coupon: <strong>LEBFREE</strong></li><li>$1/month after</li><li><a href=\"https://virmach.com/manage/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=7\">Order here</a></li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"><strong>Special #2</strong><p></p><ul><li>1 CPU core</li><li>128MB RAM</li><li>5GB SSD space</li><li>100GB traffic</li><li>10Mbps uplink</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>OpenVZ/SolusVM</li><li>Coupon: <strong>LEBSAVE1</strong></li><li>$1.95/month</li><li><a href=\"https://virmach.com/manage/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=1\">Order here</a></li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"><strong>Special #3</strong><p></p><ul><li>1 CPU core</li><li>512MB RAM</li><li>25GB SSD space</li><li>250GB traffic</li><li>100Mbps uplink</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>OpenVZ/SolusVM</li><li>Coupon: <strong>LEBSAVE3</strong></li><li>$3.95/month</li><li><a href=\"https://virmach.com/manage/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=3\">Order here</a></li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"><strong>Special #4</strong><p></p><ul><li>2 CPU cores</li><li>1GB RAM</li><li>2GB Burst</li><li>50GB SSD space</li><li>500GB traffic</li><li>1Gbps uplink</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>OpenVZ/SolusVM</li><li>Coupon: <strong>LEBSAVE5</strong></li><li>$6.95/month</li><li><a href=\"https://virmach.com/manage/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=4\">Order here</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><p><span id=\"more-5475\"></span></p><p>VirMach accepts payments via PayPal and credit cards through Stripe. Short ToS: no mass mailing servers, high-cpu scripts, spamming, hacking, DDoS-ing, or anything illegal in the United States. Please read their full <a href=\"http://virmach.com/terms-conditions/\">Terms of Service</a> before you order!</p><p><strong>Network Information</strong></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">ColoCrossing \u2013 Buffalo, New York, USA</span><br>\nTest IPv4: 23.95.15.6<br>\nTest file: <a href=\"http://23.95.15.6/1GB.zip\">http://23.95.15.6/1GB.zip</a></p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fvirmach-first-month-free-vps-1month-after-and-more-starting-at-1-95month-for-128mb-in-buffalo%2F&amp;t=VirMach%20-%20First%20month%20free%20VPS%20%28%241%2Fmonth%20after%29%20and%20more%20starting%20at%20%241.95%2Fmonth%20for%20128MB%20in%20Buffalo\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.co